### Hello!

# Interested in attending or speaking at Women Who Code's Lightning Talks?

## Deets
Where: Coming soon!

When: Later this year!

Who: You! And other fantastic technical women.

What: 5-6 minute talks on anything relating to the tech industry 
- the sweet hack you put together to solve a problem
- what you wished you knew at the beginning/middle/yesterday of your career
- an awesome new tool or language you've been using
- reflections on state of the tech industry

## Being a Speaker
Form link coming soon
